      "invariant_justification": "This is a contractual and integration policy constraint, not a physical invariant. It can be relaxed once partners migrate, but violating it before migration breaks partner integrations.",
      "testable_assertion": "Partner API responses for shipments (including multi-recipient ones) must serialize in the legacy single-recipient format unless the partner has opted into the new format."
