      "scenario": "A Shipment is in-transit and a new Recipient is added",
      "expected_behavior": "This depends on the Shipment lifecycle state. Adding recipients to an already-dispatched shipment may require re-routing. The system should enforce state-dependent rules about when recipients can be modified."
